<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Jesuh, Khamhtu, ka hruai tuah, Nun caan thlichia tho chungin, Tilet
 nih a ka khuh lai, Lungpang le ti-hrual chungah, Lam ding nang nih ka
 hmuhsak, Jesuh Khamhtu ka hruai tuah,

[V2]
 Sunghno nih nau a awih bang, Rilipi cu na awih khawh, Tilet nih na
 nawl an ngaih, &quot;Dai u,&quot; na ti i an dai, Rili cungah nawlngeitu, Jesuh
 Khamhtu ka hruai tuah,

[V3]
 Ti kam he kaa naih tikah, Tihnung tilet thawng a thang, Na tang ah na
 ka pom i, Dai tein kaa dinhnak hnga, &quot;Tih hlah! atu kan hruai lai,&quot; ti na
 aw-nem ka theihter.</lyrics>
<key>Bb</key>
<title>JESUH, KHAMHTU, KA HRUAI TUAH CH47</title>
<hymn_number>47</hymn_number>
</song>